OL,6,FWords by Joseph Wardropper, ITV News
OL,7,FSenior Producer
OL,9,FSaudi Arabia has been officially
OL,10,Fawarded the 2034 World Cup during a
OL,11,F"virtual" meeting of Fifa's 211
OL,12,Fmembers.
OL,14,FThe Gulf kingdom has been seen as the
OL,15,Fde facto host since October 2023, when
OL,16,FAustralia pulled out of the running
OL,17,Fafter Fifa gave them less than four
OL,18,Fweeks to declare their bid.
