OL,6,FFifa's member nations voted at the
OL,7,Fsame time to award the 2030 World Cup
OL,8,Fto Morocco, Spain and Portugal, in the
OL,9,Ffirst uncontested bidding process for
OL,10,Fmore than half a century.
OL,12,FGianni Infantino, Fifa's president,
OL,13,Fhailed the decision as a "historic
OL,14,Fcompromise" that "unites the world."
OL,16,F"I fully trust our hosts to address
OL,17,Fall open points in this process and
OL,18,Fdeliver a World Cup that meets the
OL,19,Fworld's expectations," he said.
