OL,6,F"The FA Board met the Saudi Arabian
OL,7,FFootball Federation last month to
OL,8,Fdiscuss their bid in more detail," the
OL,9,FFA said in a statement.
OL,11,F"We asked them to commit to ensuring
OL,12,Fall fans would be safe and welcome in
OL,13,FSaudi Arabia in 2034 ` including
OL,14,FLGBTQ+ fans. They assured us that they
OL,15,Fare fully committed to providing a
OL,16,Fsafe and welcome environment for all
OL,17,Ffans.''
