OL,6,FBefore the 2022 World Cup in
OL,7,Fneighbouring Qatar, the FA was one of
OL,8,Ften European Football Associations to
OL,9,Fpress Fifa to create a compensation
OL,10,Ffund for migrant workers and to
OL,11,Frespect human rights and the safety of
OL,12,FLGBTQ+ fans.
OL,14,FAhead of Wednesday's online meeting,
OL,15,Fthe Norwegian Football Federation
OL,16,F(NFF) criticised the "flawed and
OL,17,Finconsistent" bidding process, writing
OL,18,Fto Fifa to demand "greater
OL,19,Ftransparency, fairness, and stricter
OL,20,Fadherence to Fifa's 2016 reforms".
