OL,6,FResponding to the NFF's letter,
OL,7,FMattias Grafstrom, Fifa Secretary
OL,8,FGeneral, promised to address all
OL,9,Fcomplaints after the congress.
OL,11,FFifa did not confirm whether the 2034
OL,12,FWorld Cup would be played in winter,
OL,13,Fas many expect, but did previously
OL,14,Fnote that "peak daytime temperatures
OL,15,Fcan exceed 40C at the hottest times of
OL,16,Fthe day in Riyadh" and that "climatic
OL,17,Fconditions" should be considered when
OL,18,Fthe tournament is scheduled.
